images.prompt: In a breathtaking tableau of sacral surrealism, a twilight huntress stands poised against a backdrop of cosmic pulse, her silhouette illuminated by the ethereal glow of a sun-behind glare, as time-locked particles dance around her, shimmering in hues of sky rose and ember, creating an enchanting atmosphere that blurs the line between reality and dream, inviting the viewer to lose themselves in the intricate details of her flowing garments and the delicate interplay of light and shadow that accentuates her fierce yet serene expression, embodying the essence of a guardian of the twilight realm.
